#: server.py:227
msgid ""
"\n"
"    该函数是CVE修复流程的第二步，必须严格按照顺序执行：\n"
"        1. 设置仓库环境，克隆官方仓库到指定目录\n"
"        2. 添加fork远程仓库\n"
"        3. 明确反馈执行结果：\n"
"           - 仓库克隆是否成功\n"
"           - 克隆目录的完整路径\n"
"           - fork远程是否添加成功\n"
"        4. 环境设置完成后可自动进入下一步\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"    This function is the second step in the CVE remediation process and "
"must be executed strictly in order:\n"
"        1. Set up the repository environment, clone the official "
"repository to the specified directory\n"
"        2. Add the fork remote repository\n"
"        3. Clearly report the execution results:\n"
"           - Whether the repository clone was successful\n"
"           - The full path of the clone directory\n"
"           - Whether the fork remote was added successfully\n"
"        4. After environment setup is completed, automatically proceed to"
" the next step\n"
"    "

